是这么没节操。。。。      </p>\n<p>果断给我父母还了苹果手机！！！(虽然是旧款，单完全够用)</p>\n", "last_modified": 1631936055, "replies": 122, "id": 802674}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 15832, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 1924, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "NCZkevin", "website": "http://blog.nczkevin.com/", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b12b2147a5f2c4afc4a1959b7d597b17?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/NCZkevin", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1435379689, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b12b2147a5f2c4afc4a1959b7d597b17?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b12b2147a5f2c4afc4a1959b7d597b17?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 124411}, "last_reply_by": "maplelin", "last_touched": 1631944839, "title": "大家预售都抢到了吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/802615", "created": 1631880430, "content": "京东一瞬间就没了", "content_rendered": "京东一瞬间就没了", "last_modified": 1631880430, "replies": 88, "id": 802615}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 8755, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "header": "Say hello to the future.", "title_alternative": "iPhone", "avatar_m